Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.83,0:02:10.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:127836,130631}Best Supporting Actress…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.04,0:02:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132049,135552}…goes to Helen Keller\Nin "The Miracle Worker"…
